def forward(self, x):
        feat = self.net(x)
        size = [int(s) for s in feat.size()[2:]]
        output = F.avg_pool2d(feat, size)
        if self.reid:
            output.squeeze_(2).squeeze_(2)
            output.div_(output.norm(p=2, dim=1, keepdim=True))
        return output
